```{r pancreas 32213589, include=FALSE}

PMID_32213589 <- RefManageR::ReadPubMed('32213589', database = 'PubMed')

citation_32213589 <- paste0(PMID_32213589$journal,' ', PMID_32213589$year, ' ', PMID_32213589$month,';', PMID_32213589$volume,'(', PMID_32213589$number,'):', PMID_32213589$pages)

PubMed_32213589 <- paste0(PubMedString, PMID_32213589$eprint)

doi_32213589 <- paste0(doiString, PMID_32213589$doi)

Sys.sleep(1)

```
